	height=&#34;264&#34;
	srcset=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/hugo%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD_hu15858465758439763034.png 480w, ../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/hugo%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD_hu17722830100017528196.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;452&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;1086px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;2-搭建博客&#34;&gt;2 搭建博客
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;21-创建博客&#34;&gt;2.1 创建博客
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;（1）在&lt;strong&gt;hugo.exe&lt;/strong&gt;所在文件夹的地址栏敲打cmd，然后Enter唤起命令行&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;&#34; &gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/1%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8cmd.png&#34;
	width=&#34;627&#34;
	height=&#34;223&#34;
	srcset=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/1%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8cmd_hu17847048786220277494.png 480w, ../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/1%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8cmd_hu10611417904628283939.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;281&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;674px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;（2）敲打命令&lt;code&gt;hugo new site xxxx&lt;/code&gt;创建hugo文件&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;&#34; &gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/2newSite.png&#34;
	width=&#34;751&#34;
	height=&#34;236&#34;
	srcset=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/2newSite_hu3122308046660715862.png 480w, ../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/2newSite_hu17054959501302615844.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;318&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;763px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;（3）敲打命名&lt;code&gt;cd xxxx&lt;/code&gt;切换目录，并把&lt;strong&gt;hugo.exe&lt;/strong&gt;复制到刚生成的文件夹中&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;&#34; &gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/3cd.png&#34;
	width=&#34;842&#34;
	height=&#34;409&#34;
	srcset=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/3cd_hu914900251781706643.png 480w, ../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/3cd_hu7455587607991263771.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;205&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;494px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;（4）敲打命令&lt;code&gt;hugo server -D&lt;/code&gt;启动服务，访问&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;http://localhost:1313&lt;/a&gt;，Ctrl+C停止服务 &lt;strong&gt;（hugo默认是没有主题的，需要进行主题配置）&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;&#34; &gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/4server.png&#34;
	width=&#34;749&#34;
	height=&#34;466&#34;
	srcset=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/4server_hu759523152192672934.png 480w, ../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/4server_hu3105970367046092981.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;160&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;385px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;&#34; &gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/5pageNotFind.png&#34;
	width=&#34;535&#34;
	height=&#34;277&#34;
	srcset=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/5pageNotFind_hu14142279337497898002.png 480w, ../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/5pageNotFind_hu3905542197507831849.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;193&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;463px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;22-配置主题&#34;&gt;2.2 配置主题
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;（1）前往【&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://themes.gohugo.io/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Hugo Themes&lt;/a&gt;】，查找自己喜欢的主题，进行下载&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;&#34; &gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/1.1hugo%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1491&#34;
	height=&#34;645&#34;
	srcset=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/1.1hugo%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD_hu3884244861959241836.png 480w, ../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/1.1hugo%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD_hu14326899821210437207.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;231&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;554px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;（2）这边以【&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/CaiJimmy/hugo-theme-stack/tags&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Stack主题&lt;/a&gt;】为例，将下载好的主题解压，放到&lt;code&gt;/themes&lt;/code&gt;文件夹中&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;&#34; &gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/1.2%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E8%A7%A3%E5%8E%8B.png&#34;
	width=&#34;534&#34;
	height=&#34;453&#34;
	srcset=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/1.2%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E8%A7%A3%E5%8E%8B_hu18019446707079695737.png 480w, ../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/1.2%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E8%A7%A3%E5%8E%8B_hu8909256151664846444.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;117&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;282px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;（3）将&lt;code&gt;exampleSite&lt;/code&gt;样例数据中的 &lt;strong&gt;Content&lt;/strong&gt; 和 &lt;strong&gt;hugo.yaml&lt;/strong&gt; 复制到主文件夹中，并删掉&lt;code&gt;hugo.toml&lt;/code&gt;和&lt;code&gt;content/post/rich-content&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;&#34; &gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/1.3%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E5%A4%8D%E5%88%B61.png&#34;
	width=&#34;296&#34;
	height=&#34;251&#34;
	srcset=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/1.3%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E5%A4%8D%E5%88%B61_hu14737932469267142275.png 480w, ../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/1.3%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E5%A4%8D%E5%88%B61_hu6233231816324566059.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;117&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;283px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;&#34; &gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/1.4%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E5%A4%8D%E5%88%B62.png&#34;
	width=&#34;374&#34;
	height=&#34;244&#34;
	srcset=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/1.4%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E5%A4%8D%E5%88%B62_hu3670930292275600289.png 480w, ../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/1.4%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E5%A4%8D%E5%88%B62_hu16263024395150776200.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;153&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;367px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;（4）修改 &lt;strong&gt;hugo.yaml&lt;/strong&gt; 中的 &lt;strong&gt;theme&lt;/strong&gt;，将他修改为跟主题文件夹同名&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;&#34; &gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/1.5%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E5%90%8D%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9.png&#34;
	width=&#34;457&#34;
	height=&#34;375&#34;
	srcset=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/1.5%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E5%90%8D%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9_hu16474799724051967686.png 480w, ../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/1.5%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E5%90%8D%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9_hu14466086748644176880.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;121&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;292px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;（5）再次启动hugo服务，查看主题，具体主题配置修改 &lt;strong&gt;hugo.yaml&lt;/strong&gt;，这里不细说，感兴趣可自行查找相关文章&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;&#34; &gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/stack%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1912&#34;
	height=&#34;987&#34;
	srcset=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/stack%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98_hu13058455221565664461.png 480w, ../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/stack%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98_hu13097401748800935351.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;193&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;464px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;3-github部署&#34;&gt;3 Github部署
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;31-常规部署&#34;&gt;3.1 常规部署
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;（1）前往【&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Github官网&lt;/a&gt;】，创建仓库 &lt;strong&gt;{github用户名}.github.io&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;&#34; &gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/github%E4%BB%93%E5%BA%93%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA.png&#34;
	width=&#34;683&#34;
	height=&#34;163&#34;
	srcset=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/github%E4%BB%93%E5%BA%93%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA_hu13636233454874534047.png 480w, ../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/github%E4%BB%93%E5%BA%93%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA_hu14029540066389114074.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;419&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;1005px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;（2）前往&lt;code&gt;Setting -&amp;gt; Pages -&amp;gt; Branch&lt;/code&gt;选择main分支，然后保存，会自动开启 &lt;strong&gt;https://{github用户名}.github.io&lt;/strong&gt; 的地址，这地址也是以后访问博客的地址&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;&#34; &gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/githubPage%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8.png&#34;
	width=&#34;872&#34;
	height=&#34;555&#34;
	srcset=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/githubPage%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8_hu7152301421823947195.png 480w, ../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/githubPage%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8_hu1901808604315730425.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;157&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;377px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;（3）回到hugo文件中，执行命令&lt;code&gt;hugo -D&lt;/code&gt;，会生成 &lt;strong&gt;public&lt;/strong&gt; 静态资源文件夹&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;&#34; &gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E9%9D%99%E6%80%81%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6.png&#34;
	width=&#34;698&#34;
	height=&#34;556&#34;
	srcset=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E9%9D%99%E6%80%81%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6_hu13746208741483579646.png 480w, ../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E9%9D%99%E6%80%81%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6_hu4371999441949824785.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;125&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;301px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;（4）在 &lt;strong&gt;public&lt;/strong&gt; 执行以下命令上传到github仓库上，第一次上传可能需要输入账号密码&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;table&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;2
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;3
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;4
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;5
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;6
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;（5）上传成功后访问 &lt;strong&gt;https://{github用户名}.github.io&lt;/strong&gt;，成功搭建属于自己的Hugo博客&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;32-github-action自动部署&#34;&gt;3.2 Github Action自动部署
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;（1）Github创建一个新的仓库，用于存放Hugo的主文件&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;（2）前往&lt;code&gt;Setttings -&amp;gt; Developer Settings -&amp;gt; Personal access tokens&lt;/code&gt;，创建一个token(classic)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;&#34; &gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/createToken1.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1462&#34;
	height=&#34;359&#34;
	srcset=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/createToken1_hu3225163424929124414.png 480w, ../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/createToken1_hu8495560841693532671.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;407&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;977px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;（3）token选择永不过期，并勾选 &lt;strong&gt;repo&lt;/strong&gt; 和 &lt;strong&gt;workflow&lt;/strong&gt; 选项&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;&#34; &gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/createToken2.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1050&#34;
	height=&#34;637&#34;
	srcset=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/createToken2_hu6150244707236553172.png 480w, ../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/createToken2_hu13315092729391035093.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;164&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;395px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;（4）为保证安全，将生成的token，保存的仓库的变量中，前往&lt;code&gt;Settings -&amp;gt; Secrets and variables -&amp;gt; Actions&lt;/code&gt;中设置&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;&#34; &gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/createToken3.png&#34;
	width=&#34;842&#34;
	height=&#34;312&#34;
	srcset=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/createToken3_hu8435878091243039327.png 480w, ../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/createToken3_hu4691990066752145827.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;269&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;647px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;&#34; &gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/setToken1.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1222&#34;
	height=&#34;712&#34;
	srcset=&#34;../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/setToken1_hu4815040327071206833.png 480w, ../../p/hugo-github-builder/index.assets/setToken1_hu3578400413721326659.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;171&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;411px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;（5）在hugo主文件创建一个&lt;code&gt;.github/workflows/xxxx.yaml&lt;/code&gt;文件，将以下内容复制进去，想具体了解更多，可查看【&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://docs.github.com/zh/actions&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Github Action文档&lt;/a&gt;】&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;
&lt;table class=&#34;lntable&#34;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt; 1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt; 2
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt; 3
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt; 4
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt; 5
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt; 6
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt; 7
